entries.femaleVariant: Cecil! I know he's in there. Saw 'im crawl in your tent!
Gonna come in, kick your ass, then kick that damn cat's ass.
No way, ya bastard! He's my cat now! You never loved 'im!
Zip it open! Now! Or we boot your ass out of here!
Go on an' try, bitch. Whole 'hood ain't nothin' but empty hotels anyways.
I'ma set myself up in a penthouse suite, you'll see.
Hah! Gonna crawl your ass up them empty stairs? You an' those ganic knees o' yours?
Will ya get off my ass! And shut the fuck up about my knees!
Y'all can go wake up someone else every five minutes.
